WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.800
1. Welcome to our photo club.

00:05.800 --> 00:12.600
Do you like taking photos? Would you like to learn more about how to take good photos?

00:12.600 --> 00:20.300
Or how to make them better? Come to our photo club on Thursday evening and find out.

00:20.300 --> 00:25.900
2. Dance to the music of the world.

00:25.900 --> 00:32.000
Have you ever listened to music from Africa or South America?

00:32.000 --> 00:37.800
Do you like American pop or rock? And do you like to dance?

00:37.800 --> 00:42.900
If you love listening to music from countries all around the world,

00:42.900 --> 00:46.000
come along every Wednesday evening.

00:46.000 --> 00:52.000
Listen to new songs and learn how to dance.

00:52.000 --> 00:55.000
3. Film Night

00:55.100 --> 00:59.800
Tuesday night is film night. Come and watch the latest films.

00:59.800 --> 01:07.300
Enjoy them with your friends. Talk about them all without going to a cinema in the city centre.

01:07.300 --> 01:12.000
A. Jack plays the guitar really well,

01:12.000 --> 01:15.100
but he would like to play with some other people.

01:15.100 --> 01:20.600
He also likes dancing, but has no one to dance with.

01:20.600 --> 01:22.300
B.

01:22.400 --> 01:26.600
Annie has just received a new camera for her birthday,

01:26.600 --> 01:31.900
but she does not know how to use it and would like to learn more.

01:31.900 --> 01:33.900
C.

01:33.900 --> 01:40.000
Dan usually spends his evening watching films on television and DVDs.

01:40.000 --> 01:43.300
He lives a long way from the city centre,

01:43.300 --> 01:47.300
and his parents would like him to make some new friends.

